SQL-Structured Query Language

MYSQL - Database

Types of commands in MYSQL

1)
DDL->Data Definition Language
=>Create,alter,drop,truncate,rename

2)
DML->Data Manipulation Language
=>insert,update,delete

3)
DQL->Data Query Language
=>select

4)
DCL->Data Control Language
=>rollback,commit

->Query

->Software:XAMPP

->Functions:
1)Scalar Function:

MID: SELECT MID(NAME,1,4) FROM Students; 


2)Agreegate Function:
AVG: SELECT AVG(salary)FROM details;

FIRST: SELECT salary FROM details ORDER BY salary ASC LIMIT 1;
LAST:SELECT salary FROM details ORDER BY salary DESC LIMIT 1;

Views:
Create view myview as select colname from tablename



